<textHTML>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sort the cards to create ionic compounds, attempting to maximize the number of points obtained (according to the &lt;a href="https://www.saltise.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Chemicards_Instructions.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;"IONIC!" card rules&lt;/a&gt; developed by Petosa &amp;amp; Brouillette)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Post a photo of the sorted card into an online collaborative platform (e.g. Visual Classrooms)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Below the photo, write a paragraph indicating the number of points obtained and what ion pairs result in points&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
